<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink63-kilavi">
      <p type="edition">parattaiyiṟ pirintuvanta talaimakaṉōṭu talaimakaḷ pulantu kūṟiyatu.
      </p>
      <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="Aink63">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>poykaip paḷḷip pulavunāṟu nīrnāy</l>
<l>vāḷai nāḷirai peṟūu mūra</l>
<l>vennalan tolaiva tāyiṉun</l>
<l>tuṉṉalam perumapiṟart tōynta mārpē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">


<l>   O man from a village! </l> 
<l rend="indent2"> 	Where an otter, </l> 
<l rend="indent4"> 	reeking of rotten fish,</l> 
<l rend="indent6"> 	from his lair in the pond</l> 
<l rend="indent8"> 	catches Vāḷai fish</l> 
<l rend="indent8"> 	for [his] daily prey – </l> 
<l> Although we have lost our virtue, </l> 
<l> we shall not approach, </l> 
<l> o big man, </l> 
<l> [your] chest that others have touched. </l> 


</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
